    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/6d3a68af91737f18f1e00e49bdba3cb6.webp?t=1731813467\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras_big/6d3a68af91737f18f1e00e49bdba3cb6.webp?t=1731813467 width=800 height=3 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/aa1387083c6f768e8d7b0b5f89413d65.avif?t=1731813467\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras_big/aa1387083c6f768e8d7b0b5f89413d65.avif?t=1731813467 width=800 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/f8d96e21358fdef04abdaf6dc0448bbd.avif?t=1731813467\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras_big/f8d96e21358fdef04abdaf6dc0448bbd.avif?t=1731813467 width=800 height=71 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A demon, hellbent on destruction. An exorcist, determined that light will prevail.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Which will you be tonight?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From TurboMassiveGames comes <strong>NightingNail</strong>, an enthralling 1v1 PvP experience set in a beautifully stylized gothic world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/ba1348b7e454e3625573b195f85a0ad6.avif?t=1731813467\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras_big/ba1348b7e454e3625573b195f85a0ad6.avif?t=1731813467 width=800 height=71 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/9e6603fb14ddf73c050bf0f9d71c0b68.poster.avif?t=1731813467\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/9e6603fb14ddf73c050bf0f9d71c0b68.webm?t=1731813467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/9e6603fb14ddf73c050bf0f9d71c0b68.mp4?t=1731813467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/600095ee9d4b87b3ccee78d9bfe45d4e.avif?t=1731813467\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras_big/600095ee9d4b87b3ccee78d9bfe45d4e.avif?t=1731813467 width=800 height=121 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/da4bfcf18a002a5ee124c5bfb90fb091.avif?t=1731813467\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras_big/da4bfcf18a002a5ee124c5bfb90fb091.avif?t=1731813467 width=800 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into this atmospheric world where deception reigns. <strong>NightingNail</strong> is a game of cunning, strategy, and chaos, where outsmarting your opponent is key to survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/94ac9cfeae1e1c23976e3d41793cd077.avif?t=1731813467\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras_big/94ac9cfeae1e1c23976e3d41793cd077.avif?t=1731813467 width=800 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/aeaae3ce447745bc65b7aadcc58117c7.poster.avif?t=1731813467\" width=800 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/aeaae3ce447745bc65b7aadcc58117c7.webm?t=1731813467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Fend off evil as the Exorcist</strong>: A holy figure tasked with protecting innocent villagers. Seek out the evil lurking within the shadows, casting spells and laying ambushes. Use your wit and skill to expose the demon concealed in your midst.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Or embrace your darker nature as the Demon</strong>: A sinister creature of stealth and malevolence, armed with a sharpened nail of unholy proportions. Stab, outrun, and kill your way to victory, bringing hell to earth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/c0945ae1341e8af0ce5f191b9ebe67e5.poster.avif?t=1731813467\" width=800 height=371 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/c0945ae1341e8af0ce5f191b9ebe67e5.webm?t=1731813467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this gothic game of hide and seek, each player must defeat the other in intense one-on-one battles. Each and every choice can lead to triumph, or to defeat. The demon must claim a  number of villagers' lives - all the while at risk of being discovered by the exorcist. The exorcist must uncover the demon's identity before he takes the lives of the innocents - the village’s very survival hangs in a precarious balance.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/418bb37b75e0f0596c0e2e1d9bbabac5.avif?t=1731813467\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras_big/418bb37b75e0f0596c0e2e1d9bbabac5.avif?t=1731813467 width=800 height=100 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Abilities</strong>: Harness your character's distinct powers to outmaneuver your opponent. How will you secure victory tonight?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intense PvP</strong>: Challenge your friends (and foes) in thrilling 1v1 matches to determine the ultimate victor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stunning Visuals</strong>: Crafted in Unreal Engine 5, explore a beautifully designed gothic world that enhances your gameplay experience.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ready to fight?</strong> Wishlist <strong>NightingNail</strong> and stay updated by following our social media pages!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/6d3a68af91737f18f1e00e49bdba3cb6.webp?t=1731813467\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras_big/6d3a68af91737f18f1e00e49bdba3cb6.webp?t=1731813467 width=800 height=3 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/ecd69f237510dcdbb6ede9e7defe9f31.poster.avif?t=1731813467\" width=800 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199110/extras/ecd69f237510dcdbb6ede9e7defe9f31.webm?t=1731813467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
